data.description: Discover comfort and style in this 3-bed, 2-bath end unit townhome spanning 1290 sq ft. Embrace modern living with a well-appointed kitchen, inviting living spaces, and a private backyard. The spacious layout is perfect for gatherings, and the end unit location provides an extra layer of privacy. With three bedrooms, this home is ideal for families or those desiring extra space. Experience the perfect blend of functionality and charm in this thoughtfully designed townhome. Owner is a licensed Real Estate Broker
